    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once the pan is hot, add your <strong>basa fillet[s]</strong> and pour over your <strong>soy sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
