    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the basa is cooking, drain and roughly chop your <strong>pineapple</strong></p><p>Tip: Don’t chuck pineapple juice down the drain. Instead, add it to your smoothies, cakes or marinades!</p><p>Trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span></strong>finely</p><p>Wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper<strong> </strong>and shred</p><p>Chop your <strong>coriander</strong> roughly, including the stalks</p>",
