    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped pineapple</strong>, <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>spring onion</strong> and <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>coriander</strong> to a bowl and gently mix it all together – this is your <strong>speedy pineapple salsa</strong></p>",
