    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the fish is cooked, break it apart into bite-sized pieces with a wooden spoon and remove from the heat – these are your <strong>blackened basa chunks</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>tortillas</strong> to a plate and pop them in the <strong>microwave </strong>for 1-2 min or until warmed through</p>",
